-- =====================================================
-- Alabama (AL) Medical Malpractice Rules
-- Enhanced Verification Protocol v2.0
-- =====================================================
-- State: Alabama
-- Governing Law: Alabama Medical Liability Act of 1987 (Ala. Code § 6-5-480 et seq.)
-- Negligence Model: CONTRIBUTORY NEGLIGENCE (complete bar — one of 4 remaining states)
-- SOL: 2 years (Ala. Code § 6-5-482); 4-year statute of repose
-- Damage Caps: § 6-5-544 cap struck down as unconstitutional; NO effective non-economic cap
-- Expert: Same specialty, licensed and practicing in year preceding malpractice (§ 6-5-548)
-- =====================================================

-- RULE 1: STANDARD OF CARE
